node.text: #ChaseVisaAmbassador Tapping to ride on the @mta with my Chase Visa card makes it so much easier to get around when I’m in the city. The best part is @chase and @visa_us us will donate $.10 to @newyorkcares to give back to the local community and help the best fans in the world (New Yorkers) return to public transit safely. Chase and Visa will donate $.10 per qualifying Chase Visa contactless card transaction (excluding mobile wallet transactions) made for a single ride fare with the MTA within NYC, up to a maximum donation of $250,000. Ends 9/30/2021 or when maximum donation amount is reached. For more info about New York Cares: www.NewYorkCares.org
